title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Sep 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Sep 23 2022
description:
New movie, The Woman King, rewrites the history of slavery in Africa, part of the world Buck studied when joining the CIA as a former intelligence officer. Dr. Saphier drops truth bomb on Stacey Abrams' fetal heartbeat lie. Beyond Meat CEO bites somebody's nose. Surgeon General says he likes to eat cones without ice cream. Former Trump WH Official Roma Daravi joins Clay and Buck to discuss whether President Trump will run, the horrible job Biden is doing, and the uprising in Iran -- and pistachio ice cream.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
